PK PKER PVP "PLAYER KILLER"

Usage: ^gTOGGLE PK^n

The player killer flag allows you to enter in player vs player
combat without suffering any penalties. This however only extends
to other players who have also toggled the PK flag. You must be out
of Newbie status to toggle this. This flag cannot be removed once
it has been toggled on.

^WSee Also: TOGGLE, KILLER, NEWBIE^n
